---
title: Eggplant & Kumara Thai Green Curry with Makrut Lime Rice
description: With its gentle warming heat and colourful veggies, a rich and creamy Thai curry is a favourite meal for good reason! Whip up this version with eggplant, broccoli and kumara, plus aromatic rice made with makrut lime leaves and embrace a modern classic.
